      <title>贝莱德即将收购私人信贷管理公司 HPS</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/blackrock-said-to-be-near-deal-to-buy-private-credit-manager-hps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 即将达成收购 HPS Investment Partners 的交易，此次收购将使该公司跻身私人信贷领域的顶级行列，而该公司正寻求成为另类资产领域的一支主力军。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/blackrock-said-to-be-near-deal-to-buy-private-credit-manager-hps</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 20:13:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stellantis 首席执行官 Tavares 辞职并移交给临时委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/stellantis-ceo-tavares-set-to-step-down-from-jeep-fiat-maker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受利润下滑和美国市场销量疲软的影响，Stellantis NV 首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯 (Carlos Tavares) 决定辞职。这家吉普 SUV 和菲亚特轿车制造商将由董事长约翰·埃尔坎 (John Elkann) 领导的临时委员会管理公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/stellantis-ceo-tavares-set-to-step-down-from-jeep-fiat-maker</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 18:51:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据路透社报道，孟加拉国希望重新谈判阿达尼电力交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/bangladesh-wants-to-renegotiate-adani-power-deal-reuters-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社援引孟加拉国电力部部长的话报道，如果该协议不被法院取消，孟加拉国希望与阿达尼集团重新谈判电力购买协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/bangladesh-wants-to-renegotiate-adani-power-deal-reuters-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 17:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
