      <title>Holcim 以 10 亿美元的价格将尼日利亚子公司出售给华新水泥</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/holcim-sells-nigerian-unit-to-huaxin-cement-at-1-billion-value</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士建筑材料公司 Holcim AG 同意将其尼日利亚业务出售给中国华新水泥股份有限公司，交易价值为 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/holcim-sells-nigerian-unit-to-huaxin-cement-at-1-billion-value</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 09:09:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风暴和罢工过后美国就业增长有望迅速回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/us-job-growth-due-for-snapback-after-storms-and-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在飓风和大规模罢工削弱了上个月的就业增长之后，美国 11 月份的招聘人数可能出现增长，这与劳动力市场健康但逐渐降温的状况相一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/us-job-growth-due-for-snapback-after-storms-and-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
